
# Chromium run error

FATAL:zygote_host_impl_linux.cc(124)] No usable sandbox! Update your kernel 


do the following

https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/src/+/master/docs/linux/suid_sandbox_development.md

sudo chown root:root chrome_sandbox && sudo chmod 4755 chrome_sandbox && \
    export CHROME_DEVEL_SANDBOX="$PWD/chrome_sandbox"
./chrome



# chrome play video with no sound

  dmesg shows Linux kernel probe codecs with no result
  
  recompile kernel with various codecs options checked

